- [ ] What is the task? :: $1
- [ ] Do you have something to drink?
- [ ] Are distractions closed?
  - [ ] Shut the door (if relevant)
  - [ ] dnd phone, close twitter/gmail/reddit tabs
- [ ] Select and play music
- [ ] Why are you doing this task? :: $2
- [ ] What are the parts to this task?
  - $3
- [ ] What's an achievable goal for this sitting? :: $4
- [ ] How long will you work until you take a break? :: $5
